  "response": "Indian web development companies find international gigs through several strategies:\n\n1. Online Platforms\n- Upwork\n- Freelancer.com\n- Toptal\n- PeoplePerHour\n- Freelance websites\n\n2. Networking\n- LinkedIn professional connections\n- Global tech conferences\n- Industry meetups\n- Online tech forums\n- Professional networking events\n\n3. B2B Marketing\n- Creating professional websites showcasing portfolio\n- SEO optimization\n- Content marketing\n- Targeted digital advertising\n- Testimonials and case studies\n\n4. Referral Networks\n- Client referrals\n- Partner recommendations\n- Alumni networks\n- Previous project connections\n\n5. Outsourcing Marketplaces\n- Clutch.co\n- GoodFirms\n- IT outsourcing platforms\n- B2B service directories\n\n6. Cold Outreach\n- Email marketing\n- Direct LinkedIn outreach\n- Targeted business proposals\n- Strategic partnerships\n\n7. Specialized Platforms\n- Global technology marketplaces\n- IT outsourcing websites\n- Industry-specific platforms\n\n8. Reputation Building\n- High-quality work\n- Competitive pricing\n- Strong communication skills\n- Demonstrating technical expertise\n\n9. Government Export Promotion\n- NASSCOM support\n- Trade missions\n- Export promotion schemes\n\nThese diverse strategies help Indian web development companies attract international clients.",
